data.description: Buy with peace of mind. New roof and Fresh paint! Solid hardwood floors were just polished! Home is located in Madison Glen that offers low HOA fee, mature trees, sidewalks, driveways and playground.   Approximately 30 minutes to RDU Airport and even less to Downtown Durham. EXPECT to fall in LOVE with this LUXURY Home. 5 bedrooms and 4 full baths! This immaculate home has it ALL!!  Large mother-in-law suite, an OPEN floorplan with Formal Dining Area, large foyer with open staircase, and a large living space great for entertaining! Beautiful hard surface flooring throughout the main level, LARGE Beautiful kitchen with meticulously maintained oak cabinets, Stainless Steel appliances, and GRANITE countertops. Don't miss the paved patio right off the mother-in-law suite. Relax in the Family Rm by the cozy gas-log fireplace. SPACIOUS Master bedroom with WALK-IN Closet. Large TV and Chairs convey in the Theatre Room.
